videos.Title: [[ 8.5 HOURS ]] Complete SQL End to End - SQL Server Tutorial { End to End } Full Course Beginners
Note: Comprehensive SQL tutorial covering all aspects of SQL Server.
Designed for beginners to build a solid foundation in SQL Server.
Covers basic to advanced SQL concepts in a single course.

videos.Title: [[ 4 HOURS ]] SSIS Complete Tutorial  - { End to End } Full Course - SQL Server Integration Services
Note: Complete tutorial on SQL Server Integration Services (SSIS).
Covers ETL processes and data integration using SSIS.
Includes practical examples and implementation techniques.

videos.Title: [[ 3.1 HOURS ]] SSAS Complete Tutorial - End to End - SQL Server Analysis Service
Note: In-depth tutorial on SQL Server Analysis Services (SSAS).
Covers multidimensional and tabular modeling in SSAS.
Includes data modeling techniques and best practices.

videos.Title: [[ 3 HOURS ]] Data Warehouse Complete Tutorial - SQL + SSIS + SSAS + Power BI - { End to End }
Note: Complete data warehouse tutorial integrating multiple technologies.
Shows how to combine SQL, SSIS, SSAS, and Power BI in a single solution.
Demonstrates end-to-end data warehouse implementation.

videos.Title: [[ 2.5 HOURS ]] Power BI Complete Tutorial - Beginner to Pro - End to End
Note: Comprehensive Power BI tutorial for all skill levels.
Covers Power BI Desktop, Power BI Service, and mobile applications.
Includes data modeling, visualization, and publishing techniques.

videos.Title: [[ 3 HOURS ]] Complete Power BI DAX End to End  - Power BI DAX Tutorial - { End to End } Full Course
Note: In-depth tutorial focused on DAX (Data Analysis Expressions) in Power BI.
Covers basic to advanced DAX functions and formulas.
Includes practical examples and performance optimization techniques.

videos.Title: [[ 3 HOURS ]] Complete Power Query End to End - PowerBI Tutorial { End to End } Full Course Beginner
Note: Comprehensive Power Query tutorial for data transformation in Power BI.
Covers ETL techniques using M language in Power Query Editor.
Suitable for beginners learning data preparation in Power BI.

videos.Title: [[ 4.5 HOURS ]] Complete Power BI Services - { End to End } Full Course - Deployment & more
Note: Detailed tutorial on Power BI Services and deployment options.

videos.Title: [[ 4.5 HOURS ]] Complete Power BI Visuals / Charts / Dashboards - { End to End } Full Course

videos.Title: [[ 3 HOURS ]] Complete Azure Data Factory - { End to End } Full Course
Note: Comprehensive tutorial on Azure Data Factory for cloud-based ETL.
